The playpen is good to use from birth up to 13.5kg, both for sleeping and keeping the baby safe when she/he is awake and playing with their toys.  The changing table that comes with it is good to use from birth up to 10kg. It has got 2 wheels on one side, which makes the playpen easy to bring from one room to another if you need to keep an eye on your baby whilst doing chores at home. The wheels can be locked so that the playpen will safely stay in one place. The playpen is also easy to pack up and store in a corner if space is needed in the home. This playpen has sentimental value to me, but I would like to pass it on in the hope that it can be used again.
